Articles.Content:
Hi, I understand this mod as well as scatterer and EVE aren't really updated for the latest version of KSP, however I was having some issues and was hoping they were caused by something other than my game version or if not at least provide you with some useful information.

The visuals mods I'm using are OPM, this mod, scatterer and Distant Object Enhancement amongst various other mostly parts mods.

Below is an imgur album containing pictures of some issues I found as well as my full gamedata folder. My game is also lacking city lights on Kerbin though I didn't get a picture of that.

https://imgur.com/a/PSyJKUr

And dropbox link for my output log: https://www.dropbox.com/s/uc0ktxdcemge8p8/output_log.txt?dl=0

 

Thanks, keep up the great work

Edited August 1, 2018 by SirSock
@SirSock I guess you uploaded a wrong output_log. Regarding the output_log, you are playing on KSP 1.1.3 and there are different mods listed than the one shown in your screenshot

18 minutes ago, 4x4cheesecake said:

@SirSock I guess you uploaded a wrong output_log. Regarding the output_log, you are playing on KSP 1.1.3 and there are different mods listed than the one shown in your screenshot

Oops my bad, didn't realise it goes to a different location these days. This should be correct: https://www.dropbox.com/s/uc0ktxdcemge8p8/output_log.txt?dl=0

Looks like EVE and scatterer don't work pretty well with 1.4.5. I did a quick test with both mods and get the same errors in my log like yours. OPM got some issues as well but that is already known.

2 hours ago, SirSock said:

I was having some issues and was hoping they were caused by something other than my game version

After doing this test, I'm pretty sure these issues are related to the game version and not caused by anything else.
That's unfortunate, any easy fixes I could try or is it a matter of waiting for an official update?

19 minutes ago, SirSock said:

That's unfortunate, any easy fixes I could try or is it a matter of waiting for an official update?

If there is an easy fix, than I don't know about it. Waiting for an update seems to be the best solution.

I've got a strange issue where only Kerbin has clouds and aurorae, while all the others including the OPM bodies are bare.

 

I'm on 1.4.5 but I've tried as far back as 1.4.3, not sure if that's related at all. Possibly an EVE issue rather than specific to this pack since the EVE in game GUI says "invalid name" and is unresponsive, but all other visual packs I've tried I get no clouds at all.

 

Love your work Galileo, keep it up!

6 hours ago, Sir LaYz said:

I've got a strange issue where only Kerbin has clouds and aurorae, while all the others including the OPM bodies are bare.

 

I'm on 1.4.5 but I've tried as far back as 1.4.3, not sure if that's related at all. Possibly an EVE issue rather than specific to this pack since the EVE in game GUI says "invalid name" and is unresponsive, but all other visual packs I've tried I get no clouds at all.

 

Love your work Galileo, keep it up!

Logs and a screenshot of your game data, please

Sure
